      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-base mb-4">Real Change for Real People</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">[This section will feature 2-3 powerful, anonymized testimonials from your clients, highlighting their transformation.]</p>
